  "subject": "During resource resolution there occurs from time to time a ConcurrentModificationException. This leads to errors, which are hard to find.",
  "commit_message": "During resource resolution there occurs from time to time a ConcurrentModificationException. This leads to errors, which are hard to find.\n\nSimple solution is to use a ConcurrentHashMap instead, because this class is thread safe.\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3978\nSigned-off-by: Frank Kimmlingen <frank.kimmlingen@telekom.de>\nChange-Id: I68de3bc24d93a784964bc4b58caa2aeebf250e33\n",
